h5=A.hy(A.b([A.cn("The meadow of gold at the mouth of the Thajiwas glacier.","80 km from Srinagar","Sonamarg"),A.cn("An untouched bowl of pasture and pine.","42 km from Srinagar","Doodhpathri"),A.cn("A thousand-year-old shrine above the lake.","8 km from Srinagar","Shankaracharya Temple")],i2),c4,h8,d,6,h1,!0,i1,h7,h0,q,"d02",h9,h3,34.0837,74.7973,"Kashmir",5,"Srinagar's houseboats, saffron fields of Pampore, the alpine amphitheatres of Gulmarg and Pahalgam \u2014 Kashmir remains the subcontinent's most romantic landscape. We arrange cedar-panelled houseboat suites on Dal Lake, private shikara flotillas at dawn, and mountain lunches served on meadows at ten thousand feet.",32e3,4.8,942,A.b([A.dC("Priya & Arjun Malhotra","The private evening in Nishat Bagh was pure cinema. Kashmir with Aurevia is a different country.",d0,"Delhi",5),A.dC("Sofia Lindqvist","The houseboat, the kahwa, the mountains \u2014 I have never slept better anywhere.",d1,"Stockholm",4.8)],i3),"Heritage houseboats, private Mughal garden evenings and alpine meadows. 6-day Kashmir journeys by Aurevia.","Kashmir Luxury Tours \u2014 Dal Lake Houseboats, Gulmarg & Pahalgam","kashmir","A valley the poets never exaggerated",h5,c3)
