i1=A.b([A.b1(1,"Transfer to a beachfront heritage resort near Betalbatim. Evening at leisure on a quiet stretch of silver sand.","Arrival \u2014 South Goa"),A.b1(2,"Basilica of Bom Jesus and S\xe9 Cathedral at opening time, then a slow walk through the Latin Quarter with feni tasting and lunch at a heritage caf\xe9.","Old Goa & Fontainhas"),A.b1(3,"Up the Mandovi to a working spice farm \u2014 cardamom, peppercorn, betel. Traditional lunch, afternoon river cruise past mangroves.","Spice country"),A.b1(4,"Private boat to Butterfly and Honeymoon beaches. Golden hour aboard a catamaran with Goan canap\xe9s.","Islands & sunset sail"),A.b1(5,"Beach breakfast and a private transfer to Dabolim or Mopa airport.",a5)],h6)
