q=A.b([A.b1(1,"The Himalaya from your window seat, then two slow days begin. Rest, hydrate, and watch the light on Stok Kangri from your terrace.","Fly into Leh"),A.b1(2,"Gentle morning at Shanti Stupa and Leh Palace, afternoon in the old town's bakeries and antique shops.","Leh acclimatisation"),A.b1(3,"Dawn prayers at Thiksey, the Indus valley's great gompas \u2014 Hemis, Stakna, Matho \u2014 and lunch in a village orchard.","Monastery circuit"),A.b1(4,"Cross 17,582 feet into the valley of flowers. Evening among the double-humped camels on the Hunder dunes.","Over Khardung La to Nubra"),A.b1(5,"The Shyok river road to Pangong Tso. Your camp sits on the lake's western shore; dinner under a sky thick with stars.","Nubra to Pangong"),A.b1(6,"Sunrise as the lake runs through its blues, then back over Chang La with a stop at Hemis. Farewell dinner in Leh.","Pangong to Leh"),A.b1(7,"Morning flight out over the ranges.",a5)],h6)
