h7=A.hy(A.b([A.cn("The optical illusion where cars appear to roll uphill.","27 km from Leh","Magnetic Hill"),A.cn("Eleventh-century murals unmatched in the Himalaya.","66 km from Leh","Alchi Monastery"),A.cn("A remoter, wilder twin to Pangong in Changthang.","220 km from Leh","Tso Moriri")],i2),"June \u2013 September",h1,d,7,h9,!0,p,i1,h3,o,"d04",h8,q,34.1526,77.5771,"Ladakh",6,"A high-altitude desert of cobalt lakes, thousand-year-old gompas and passes that graze the sky. Our Ladakh journeys are built around acclimatisation and access \u2014 private monastery audiences, luxury camps on Pangong's shore, and drives over Khardung La with oxygen, chase vehicle and a crew that has done this a hundred times.",38500,4.9,731,A.b([A.dC("Aditya Rao","The stargazing night at Pangong rearranged something in me. Faultless organisation at brutal altitudes.","August 2025","Hyderabad",5),A.dC("Marco Bianchi","I've done Patagonia and Iceland. Ladakh with this team tops both.","July 2026","Milan",4.9)],i3),"Luxury camps, monastery audiences and oxygen-equipped expeditions across the high Himalaya.","Ladakh Expeditions \u2014 Pangong, Nubra & Khardung La in Comfort","ladakh","The last great silence",h7,c3)
